**APIWaveRadar**  
**Description:**  
Monitors and visualizes wave-like shifts in API latency, including sudden disruptions and slow pulse drifts.

```markdown
# APIWaveRadar - Latency Wave Monitor

APIWaveRadar detects undulating latency patterns in real-time and visualizes delay trends and endpoint fluctuations.

## Features
- Waveform latency analysis  
- Endpoint drift detection  
- Export logs to CSV or JSON

## Usage
```bash
git clone https://github.com/your-username/APIWaveRadar.git
cd APIWaveRadar
python monitor.py
